Package ohos.ivihardware.adas.model

Class AdasPropertyInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ivihardware.adas.model.AdasPropertyInfo

  • public class AdasPropertyInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes Advanced Driver Assistant System (ADAS) signal information.

    The information includes the ADAS signal ID, node type, data type, signal value, and zone ID, as well as whether the signal value can be set.

    Since:
    3
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Ivi.ADAS
